---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Ximius XData" sideBarActiveItemID="projects">
  <article class="grid gap-10">
    <header class="grid gap-4">
      <a class="link w-fit" href="/projects">Back to projects</a>
      <img src="/XimiusLogo.webp" alt="Ximius logo" class="max-h-28 w-fit object-contain" />
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Ximius XData - Back-End Hospital Capacity Management</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-base-content/75">
          Replace or refine this summary with the exact scope of your work, the systems involved, and the outcome you can
          publicly describe.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Project Overview</h2>
      <p>
        This project focused on large data modeling and management for hospital capacity workflows. Fill this section with
        the real business context, data constraints, client requirements, and what XData helped users analyze or decide.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">My Role</h2>
      <p>
        Describe your back-end responsibilities here: data model design, APIs, validation rules, integrations,
        performance work, deployment support, or maintenance tasks. Keep the claims precise and adjust anything that feels
        too broad.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Tools and Technologies</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc mx-6 grid gap-2">
        <li>Add primary language or framework</li>
        <li>Add database, data tools, or modeling approach</li>
        <li>Add infrastructure, testing, validation, or monitoring tools</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Links and Media</h2>
      <p>
        Add the company website, permitted repository links, screenshots, diagrams, or product images here.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
